data.description: Don't miss out on this truly exceptional home in Meadow Lakes. If you are looking for a home with incredible detail & upgrades, this one is sure to please! Windows span the entire back of the home & offer relaxing views of a custom stone patio & pond. Top-of-line Mohawk flooring. Gorgeous stone fireplace in FR. The kitchen is spectacular! Granite countertops along with extra lighting throughout. Upgraded cabinets galore+roomy pantry. HUGE island, with room for seating, will not disappoint! Sun Room is light-drenched with beautiful views. The entrance from the garage has a large coat closet and half bath. The spacious, light-filled office is tucked away at the front of the house. Closets galore upstairs. Spacious Master includes a walk-in closet, beautiful bath with linen closet, and large walk-in tiled shower. The 1248 sqft basement is ready to finish to your liking and has thousands in additions & upgrades. 200 amp service. Plumed for half bath & wet bar! Whole house central vacuum. Extra insulation was added to walls, ceilings, & plumbing throughout the home for additional sound control & lower utility costs. The garage is fully insulated and plumbed for easy installation of a heater of your choice. Upgraded fire, Co2 & security systems. FR, MB, bath, and Rear Patio have sound system installed. Many more upgrades! 1248 sq ft unfinished basement. The TV mount in the family room does NOT stay. All info, measurements, etc are approx.
